                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="font-semibold">
                            <p class="text-slate-400">Want to dig deeper into Tailwind?</p>
                            <p>
                                <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs" target="_blank" class="text-sky-500 hover:text-sky-600">Read the docs &rarr;</a>
                            </p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
